Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.61,0:00:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是廢話  但卻迫切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}字：一年級三班 小松奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我小時候起  每當說起將來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是成為一個可愛的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外就沒有其它的夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁妝！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 結婚總是需要花錢的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一點一點存起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖著三個女兒  父母可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然把那麼重要的錢匯給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:01:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你私奔了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚回來  到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要晚回來的話至少先打個電話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  你剛說什麼私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京的生活怎樣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男朋友還順利吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈美  是你幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和媽媽說了些亂七八糟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說姐姐為了和男人一起住就去了東京而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是什麼見不得人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  可以天天盡情做愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.83,0:02:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快洗澡去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想多聊幾句呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也已經洗過澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的小姑娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哪裡洗的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然就在父母面前說...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好痛  媽媽踢人...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做...做愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你現在已經是成年人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}要是我也能進東京的大學該多好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些錢你喜歡怎麼用就怎麼用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過拜託你離婚了可別回娘家來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離婚了回娘家...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別再給我添麻煩了  那就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是什麼好笑的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為她會說很擔心你呀  回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說離婚了別回娘家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一般人會說的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  我根本就還沒有結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  奈津子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太酷了  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醉了嗎  娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒醉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙給你買來了  娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰  歡迎你回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是醉得不輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別往上爬了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸和真呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸醉倒在路旁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真送他回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  伸確實喝了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真那傢伙  真是沒看出來酒量那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說是裝出來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到娜娜那樣毫無防備的醉態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.88,0:04:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來泰能過來讓她非常開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還趁亂親了人家一口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外還說了「我愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過泰一點都不驚訝的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那兩個人是在交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門開著在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你一個人收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  只要再沖洗一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那給我一塊抹布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來擦乾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰真是不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外表看不出  其實人溫柔又聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可靠卻又一點都不張揚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是律師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是結婚的話  最好就是這種類型的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  我在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰是娜娜的男人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我都有章司了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算在找到住處前先住酒店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸那裡已經住了真  太擠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以住這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要跟我們客氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不過那還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說喝醉了  不過娜娜都那麼直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰為什麼還要這樣克制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道在老家那裡還有女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來玩樂隊的男人很受那些很隨便的女人歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就算已經有女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然丟在老家不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也不是什麼很重要的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是被章司丟在老家不管！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過章司可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始  他就非常重視我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也叫我來了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是是我自己自作主張追來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是私奔了嗎？拜託你離婚了可別回娘家來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自作多情...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起住吧  奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.03,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司都那樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我願意的話  隨時都可以嫁給他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一起住和結婚是兩回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說章司剛進大學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業也要到四年後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他的錢也沒我這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚總是需要花錢的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不想做個樸素的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}字：想穿上白色日式禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定要穿可愛的新娘禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}字：也想穿上婚紗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新房也不能只有一個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的話  最好是一幢帶院子的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得是新造的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得存錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽給的30萬盡量不用存入定期存款
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外還要自己存錢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力加油的話  等章司畢業應該也能存不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}章司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一幢帶院子的別墅就交給我了  章司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}字：失去控制
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天沒法去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八公  你不在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  娜娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  這副打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去面試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛打了個電話就說讓我快點過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣  還不錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出版社
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜  宿醉還沒醒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.71,0:08:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個很有效的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出版社那種地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你進得進去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我滿足應徵條件了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是要個打雜的小苦力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是家聽都沒聽說過的小公司
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會馬上又破產倒閉吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去倒點水來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要加個「哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.22,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了和衣服相配  連說話語氣都改了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  為什麼突然決定去出版社？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然在招聘雜誌裡看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時薪不錯  每週還能休息兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得能住在東京
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是想在市中心上班的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在出版社工作不是很酷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有女強人的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女強人啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:09:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  那麼快就決心找下一份工作也是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原以為你只是嘴上說說要獨立什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是蠻認真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要工作純粹只是因為想要錢罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不管是出於哪種目的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能找到個公司好好工作 就自然而然能夠邁向獨立之路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算不算一石二鳥?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.22,0:09:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  泰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰說在找到住處前先住酒店  然後就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我有阻止過他...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然就說了句「啊  是麼」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上會在平常那家錄音室練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八要不要也來？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正晚上也沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起會有泰的鼓加入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這之前的絕對是兩種感覺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.80,0:09:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜為什麼會有那麼有活力的笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都覺得有些喜不自禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下成員都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是朝著夢想勇往直前了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  還是第一次在學校裡碰到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有沒有好好來上課啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是認認真真來上課的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要代你應到？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啊  不  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是不懂直接了當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨機應變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是傳說中的幸子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}字：怎麼這麼問！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  什麼傳說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好緊張的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是越來越可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京助那傢伙...  而且又偏偏是淳子...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好剛才那個關西口音的男人帶你應到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們好好聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看到章司了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是沒有來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才還和他在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才碰到一個好像關係很好的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好像有話要說我就先來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是  那肯定不是他女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是把章司...當作好朋友...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就都寫在你臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始我還以為你們肯定在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說章司有其他女人的時候還真是吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是最近才知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我也有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙沒告訴你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己一廂情願認為他沒有的...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別袒護他了  你可真是堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧  幸子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要放棄章司和我交往呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有拿講義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  松田在老家有女朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會爆別人的隱私
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想揍你一頓  章司
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是看錯你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  只是一直沒有機會說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是我想隱瞞...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是覺得得手的話 就可以腳踏兩隻船了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我能做出那麼高技巧的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明做不到卻又有那種欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那種曖昧不明是會傷害少女的心的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許已經傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肯定已經傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子已經迷上你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那可能只是我的自我感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她並沒有明確對我說喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那之後  我們就像以前一樣只是朋友關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心智從中學起就沒有成長過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.03,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你真是沒話說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說  我該怎麼應付才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底斷絕來往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越是去應付就會讓人家傷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是... 我們學校和打工地方都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是徹底斷絕來往...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那些事  你不應該先考慮下怎麼和奈奈說？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起奈奈  幸子更重要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒什麼需要和奈奈解釋的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果奈奈已經在懷疑你了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和幸子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前  她還嘟囔著幸子怎麼怎麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼是魔王派來的爪牙之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦  那只是虛擬的幸子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  虛擬的幸子是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想問這個問題...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  章司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你厭倦了奈奈  想要從幸子那裡得到安慰的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是淳子  說得太準確了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實幸子在的時候  我就會覺得給我很大安慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:14:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你明知道奈奈是那種很麻煩的女人卻還是出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.54,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今就不能隨便扔掉  必須交往到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我也是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有思想準備要我娶奈奈也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算進了墳墓也要在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用想那麼遠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那種魔王的信徒進同一個墳墓可就成不了佛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是幫誰的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非要說的話  那我就站在正義一方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼正義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耍我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個小太妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候把中學時期的照片爆出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  正在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是之前問你借的書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要快點還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這個什麼時候還都可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的時候也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.27,0:15:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  用不著道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是故意想要偷聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是聽到你們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體就好像被綁住一樣動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是肯定已經傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子已經迷上你了吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...先聲明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才跌倒不是為了搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  幸...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下真的要好好考慮該怎麼應付了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你越是去應付就會讓人家傷得越深
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:16:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就這樣逃走不覺得太卑鄙了嗎  佐藤公一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼  自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人家全名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  章司今天不去學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就逃課來喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來也是可想而知的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我怎麼會在Jackson呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 這就是逃避嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經開始逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起奈奈  幸子更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤公一  我去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了之後一定會做絕交宣言的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和奈奈進同一個墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.20,0:16:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本第一次見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就盡量不想和她扯上關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼就不小心就向她尋求安慰了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是正合魔王的心意了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會背叛奈奈的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川村啊  為什麼回去的時候要穿運動鞋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果不跑的話就趕不上末班車
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了　快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.13,0:17:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等　幸子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用這種表情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看她的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邊走邊說吧　行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果錯過末班車的話　我來出車費
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.77,0:18:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是絕交的話 應該說什麼怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是女朋友 只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說「讓我們分手吧」也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者說「絕交」？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就非得說那種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸子又沒有做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說她是個很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我必須得說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我．．．真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司一點錯都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己一廂情願冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直提醒自己不要妨礙你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會妨礙到章司和你女朋友的關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以．．．求你．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只做朋友就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說絕交之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司打工應該已經結束了 卻一直是錄音電話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是忘了充電了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家還想快點告訴他工作已經定好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是有外遇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,章司才不會做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發個短消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真想不通那家肯雇你的公司是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們真是太缺人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過　一邊打雜一邊學習
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幹得好的話還有可能成為正式員工哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要是成了正式員工就能拿到獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就離帶院子的別墅的夢想又近了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶院子的別墅？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的夢想就是那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　超級夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就靠我的歌賺錢來建一幢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你的那間是狗屋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果娜娜是男人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的愛情一定可以一生一世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候我常會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定就不會只有快樂的回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為愛情總是伴著傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是沉溺其中就越痛苦

